    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsswitch"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " class provides a simple interface for displaying and toggling a Boolean state, such as on/off. A switch toggles its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsswitch/3172699-state"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and sends its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscontrol/1428956-action"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " when clicked, activated through the keyboard, or tapped in the Touch Bar. "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsswitch"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " also allows dragging between states, and if "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscontrol/1428952-continuous"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", the switch sends its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscontrol/1428956-action"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " for each change in position during the drag."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use a switch to toggle significant preferences, or preferences that provide access to other controls. Avoid creating lists or tables of switches; instead, for general-purpose toggles, use an instance of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsbutton"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to display a checkbox."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsswitch"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " doesn’t use an instance of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscell"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to provide its functionality. The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscontrol/1428891-cellclass"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " class property and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscontrol/1428960-cell"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " instance property both return "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/nil-2gl"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and they ignore attempts to set a non-"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/nil-2gl"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " value."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
